# Figma MCP — Afenda Design System Rules (PAS-006)

Use when integrating Figma designs via MCP (`get_design_context`, `get_screenshot`, `use_figma`, `generate_figma_design`) into this monorepo.

**Operational authority:** [`.cursor/skills/shadcn-studio/figma-mcp-afenda.md`](../skills/shadcn-studio/figma-mcp-afenda.md)  
**Design system file:** [Afenda Brand Tokens (AdminCN)](https://www.figma.com/design/LsmtG4KiaTUi3KpjxZXHwH/Afenda-Brand-Tokens-AdminCN) · file key `LsmtG4KiaTUi3KpjxZXHwH`

**Policy:** No Figma Code Connect. Map Figma → code via manifests + primitive registry + Storybook.

