| Series | Figma collection | Modes | CSS authority | Scoped class |
|--------|------------------|-------|---------------|--------------|
| AdminCN default | **Color** | Light, Dark | `packages/shadcn-studio/src/styles/shadcn-default.css` | `:root` / `.dark` |
