| Raw anchors | **Primitives** | Value | `tokens-complete.json` | future aliasing |
| Spacing / radius | **Spacing**, **Radius** | Value | `shadcn-default.css` `@theme` | `--spacing-*`, `--radius-*` |

**SSOT JSON:** `packages/shadcn-studio/tokens-complete.json`

**Manifests:**

Figma manifest JSON files are no longer kept under `packages/shadcn-studio/src/styles`; use curated package docs, theme CSS, and Storybook verification surfaces as source evidence instead.

**Figma → code:** Use `get_variable_defs` or import-variables skill; diff against manifests. Never invent hex in components when a semantic token exists.

**After CSS edits:** `pnpm sync:package-css-dist -- --package @afenda/shadcn-studio` · `pnpm check:package-css-dist-sync`

